title: --FREE AGENT-- Open Team Spots?
body:
I'm looking for a Team/Duo that's trying to climb Elo

Been playing League Of Legends casual for two years and want to start taking it seriously.
Started a new account, Lets do this!

Can confidently play all roles except support.

replies.body: Seems interesting! I don't know if I'm qualifies I'm only silver 4 :)
My last account was silver five haha, i'm keen to duo with you. Add my account DTreats
Highest I've gotten is S2 (but now I'm stuck in low Bronze). I main Jg/Mid, and can play in any other position besides ADC.

Sweet dude, im keen to duo and climb elo with you.

I'll add you, and i'll see you on the rift !

Highest i've gotten is silver 5 :(

But i just want a team to play with.
